	<h1 class="title">将健身年卡变成单次服务，互联网服务“燃健身”是怎么想的?</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">周韶宏 崔绮雯</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-18 21:09:45 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13588/medium/13588.jpg?1439749754" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13588" data-title="《将健身年卡变成单次服务，互联网服务“燃健身”是怎么想的?》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13588/medium/13588.jpg?1439749754" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13588.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
